Nauzo Angel Area Outline
Bathhouse

Theme:
  A raunchy bathhouse in the city of Parva.

NPC's:
  A proprieter(lvl 10 merchant) and a towel boy(lvl 15 rogue)
  A big fat merchant customer lounging in the bathhouse(lvl 20 merchant)
  A scantily clad gal who is obviously a prostitue(lvl 20 rogue)

Objects:
  A bar of soap, towel, thin loincloth, the npc's will be clothed
  in some plain garb, just like a tunic and pants

Treasure:
  All NPC's will have some coins, the fat merchant will have
  a variety of currencies, while the others will only contain
  shrydes
